{"text": "He explained that this individual entity cannot be sensed through any human organ.", "fibs": ["entity"]}
{"text": "He said these (Paramãnu) could form pairs or triplets, among other combinations and unseen forces cause interaction between them.", "fibs": ["form"]}
{"text": "He conceptualised this theory around 2500 years before John Dalton (1766-1844).", "fibs": ["theory"]}
{"text": "Charaka Samhita is the oldest Ayurvedic epic of India.", "fibs": ["epic"]}
