{"text": "During this period of stagnation, pharmaceutical industry based on Ayurveda continued to exist, but it too declined gradually.", "fibs": ["period"]}
{"text": "During this time, foreign products poured in.", "fibs": ["time"]}
{"text": "As a result, indigenous traditional techniques gradually declined.", "fibs": ["result"]}
{"text": "Modern science appeared in Indian scene in the later part of the nineteenth century.", "fibs": ["science"]}
{"text": "By the mid-nineteenth century, European scientists started coming to India and modern chemistry started growing.", "fibs": ["century"]}
{"text": "From the above discussion, you have learnt that chemistry deals with the composition, structure, properties and interection of matter and is of much use to human beings in daily life.", "fibs": ["discussion"]}
{"text": "These aspects can be best described and understood in terms of basic constituents of matter that are atoms and molecules.", "fibs": ["matter"]}
{"text": "That is why, chemistry is also called the science of atoms and molecules.", "fibs": ["chemistry"]}
{"text": "Is it possible to count the number of atoms and molecules in a given mass of matter and have a quantitative relationship between the mass and the number of these particles?", "fibs": ["count"]}
{"text": "We will get the answer of some of these questions in this Unit.", "fibs": ["answer"]}
