A majority of reactions in the laboratories are carried out in solutions.", "fibs": ["majority"]}
{"text": "Therefore, it is important to understand as how the amount of substance is expressed when it is present in the solution.", "fibs": ["amount"]}
{"text": "The concentration of a solution or the amount of substance present in its given volume can be expressed in any of the following ways.", "fibs": ["concentration"]}
